title: Volcom Damn Am 2014 Day 3 - Finals & DVS Best Trick
description: Congratulations goes out to Axel Cruysberghs for winning Damn Am Volcom 2014. Another congrats goes out to Franky Villani for winning DVS Best Trick. A special thanks to every skater who destroyed the course, the spectators and industry for the support all weekend. Enjoy the semi finals, finals and DVS Best Trick in this episode. Be Sure to tune into Damn Am Atlanta may 9 - 11 and for more coverage check
